These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, singing, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, western, mystery, family
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, van, train
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the train is between the person watching family movies and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking      | camping | baking | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy  | western   | family    |
| Transport     | snowmobile     | van    | train    | trike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, chess, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, indian, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, helicopter, bus
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the indian##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the pakistani##1
7. the malaysian is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
8. the russian is between the pakistani and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | baking | chess   | drawing | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | indian     | malaysian | russian  | pakistani |
| Transport     | bus        | helicopter  | quad-bike    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, asparagus, eggplant, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, australian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, scooter, subway
1. the thai is between the person eating pepper and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the malaysian is the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person eating artichoke is in an odd position##4
6. the australian is between the person eating asparagus and the dutch##2
7. the thai is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | pepper | asparagus   | artichoke     | eggplant     |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | thai | australian   | dutch  |
| Transport     | subway      | quad-bike | scooter | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation, zombie, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop, r&b, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, sailing, soccer
1. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
2. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
5. the fan of ambient is the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of metal##1
7. the fan of r&b is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | family   | zombie     | animation |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | ambient      | metal        | hip-hop     |
| Sport         | sailing | golf | soccer | ice-hockey   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, german, british, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, skiing, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, train, bike, taxi
1. the thai is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the british is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
7. the german is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
9. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | polish   | thai   | british | german |
| Sport         | water-polo      | basketball | baseball      | skiing |
| Transport     | train | boat        | taxi       | bike  |

