.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, blueberry, cauliflower, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, collecting, card-games
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, dog, lizard
1. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | cauliflower   | grapes      | blueberry       | banana |
| Hobby   | traveling | card-games | collecting     | video-games |
| Pet     | lizard     | goat  | goldfish | dog |

