.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, epic, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, hamster, goldfish
1. the owner of the hamster is the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the person watching fantasy movies and the owner of the dog##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | almond-milk          | iced-tea | cola        |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | mystery | fantasy   | disaster     |
| Pet           | dog | fish         | goldfish         | hamster |

