.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, reading, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, pilot, chef
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, funk, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
2. the pilot is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the chef is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the fan of indie##1
5. the fan of funk is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the pilot##3
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | card-games      | reading       | traveling    |
| Job           | police-officer  | pilot  | chef | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | indie | funk         | rock    |

