.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, lemonade, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, software-developer, accountant, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: juice-polo, swimming, cycling, basketball
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the software-developer is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the project-manager is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | milk         | sprite  | lemonade     | juice         |
| Job        | project-manager | software-developer | police-officer | accountant         |
| Sport      | swimming         | cycling  | juice-polo   | basketball |

