.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, jazz, r&b, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, indonesian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, rabbit, hamster
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 2. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 4. the indonesian is between the fan of jazz and the fan of techno##2
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 6. the owner of the hamster is the fan of r&b##1
 7. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
 9. the chinese is between the fan of soul and the fan of r&b##2
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | r&b    | jazz | soul    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian | chinese  | egyptian |
| Pet           | rabbit   | hamster    | fish        | goat   |

