.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, tea, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, doctor, security-guard, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, chinese, colombian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the doctor is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the colombian is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
4. the doctor is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the doctor##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the doctor##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea                | lemonade  | cola | tea   |
| Job           | videographer | doctor | social-worker   | security-guard |
| Nationality   | malaysian         | canadian     | colombian     | chinese |

