3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan of house is between the person watching superhero movies and the fan of funk##2
6. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cranberry    | carrot  | lettuce  | nectarine |
