.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, water, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: german, egyptian, russian, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking water and the german##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
3. the russian is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
7. the german is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
8. the russian is the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the nigerian is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | water      | hot-chocolate  | iced-tea    |
| Nationality   | russian   | egyptian | nigerian | german |
| Pet           | snake      | rabbit       | hamster   | cat      |

