.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, filmmaking, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, french, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is basketball##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the russian is between the person who's sport is basketball and the chinese##2
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
8. the dutch is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | filmmaking | rock-climbing  | card-games  |
| Nationality   | french | dutch       | russian | chinese |
| Sport         | skiing   | basketball      | volleyball | biathlon       |

