.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, tennis, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
5. the person drinking water is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate    | water     | iced-tea    | soy-milk        |
| Sport       | tennis   | soccer | climbing | skateboarding |
| Transport   | roller | jet-ski      | quad-bike    | tram   |

