.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pumpkin, carrot, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, thriller, zombie, drama
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, japanese, chinese, american
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
2. the spanish is between the japanese and the person eating asparagus##2
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
5. the spanish is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
7. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating asparagus is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | pumpkin | asparagus  | orange   | carrot    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | zombie     | drama | thriller |
| Nationality   | chinese   | american | spanish | japanese   |

