4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the photographer##1
5. the australian is on the right of the dutch##1
6. the chef is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the designer##1
8. the mexican is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | singing | puzzles   | rock-climbing    | sudoku    |
| Job           | musician   | photographer    | chef | designer |
| Nationality   | mexican    | dutch | australian    | american         |

