.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, lettuce, mango, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, drawing, sudoku
4 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, frog, lizard
1. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
5. the person eating lettuce is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | mango    | lettuce    | avocado  | cherry |
| Hobby   | sudoku | collecting | fishing | drawing      |
| Pet     | turtle   | goat        | lizard   | frog       |

 